Robot Game
================================================================
Author: Shuai Huang
E-mail: shh176@ucsd.edu
Date: 4.22.2017

Description
-----------
The program is a robot game where an user is asked to initialize
the starting location and face direction a robot has and then make
a list of actions to make the robot move on a 8x8 board. When the
robot reaches the boundary of the board, user will be informed that
the movement is stopped as the robot cannot move further, and the 
final location is outputed; else, if the movement is executed 
successfully, then the final lcoation will be shown.

